&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit 1 ormore Medical Receptionists into this role for Rock Healthcare Practice basedat bothBury and the Radcliffe branch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have the following options available:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Option1: Hours of work: 37.5 (WTE) worked flexibly over 5 days (Mon-Fri) between 8am-6.30pm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Option2: Hours of work: two staff members working a total of up to52.5 hours over 5 days (Mon-Fri) covering 8am-6.30pm each day&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rock Healthcare is a long established, forward thinking and dynamic GP Practice currently serving around 9,500 Patients. We are based in Moorgate Primary Care Centre in Bury as well as Radcliffe Primary Care Centre, both of which are modern, purpose-built premises containing a variety of primary care services to meet the needs of the local population.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a strong teaching and training ethos and real desire to develop potential in everyone who works for Rock Healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
